// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0363 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: de89433e-3350-596f-9b00-c8523c266949

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
